<subSubSection id="20BC6569FFD52979701AE6EB3A6AFDD4" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph id="681936E2FFD52979701AE6EB3A6AFDD4" blockId="2.[136,1059,402,587]" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">
<materialsCitation id="D8CE3CBFFFD52979701AE6EB3A26FE74" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">
5 ♂ 
<typeStatus id="B71D8840FFD529797025E6EC3AE6FE33" box="[632,725,404,428]" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">syntypes</typeStatus>
(box 17) with two handwritten labels: &quot;♂ 
<collectingRegion id="AA62F800FFD529797310E6CB39B8FE54" box="[333,395,435,459]" country="Brazil" name="Bahia" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">Bahia</collectingRegion>
blanca Rep. Arg. env. G. Claraz&quot; and &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD52979711FE6CB395AFE74" authority="Blanch." authorityName="Blanchard" authorityYear="1851" class="Insecta" family="Coptopterygidae" genus="Coptopteryx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="crenaticollis">Coptopteryx crenaticollis Blanch.</taxonomicName>
&quot; (green paper).
</materialsCitation>
The specimens were placed in the collection as “ 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD529797282E68C39C4FD94" authority="Blanchard" authorityName="Blanchard" authorityYear="1851" box="[223,503,499,523]" class="Insecta" family="Coptopterygidae" genus="Coptopteryx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="crenaticollis">
<emphasis id="5AD2EAF0FFD529797282E68C39B1FD94" box="[223,386,499,523]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">C. crenaticollis</emphasis>
Blanchard
</taxonomicName>
” because Saussure (1870) considered 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD5297971CCE68C3C11FD94" authorityName="Saussure" authorityYear="1869" box="[913,1058,499,523]" class="Insecta" family="Coptopterygidae" genus="Coptopteryx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="claraziana">
<emphasis id="5AD2EAF0FFD5297971CCE68C3C11FD94" box="[913,1058,499,523]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">C. claraziana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
a junior synonym of this species. “ 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD529797019E56C3AD4FDB4" authorityName="Blanchard" authorityYear="1851" box="[580,743,531,555]" class="Insecta" family="Coptopterygidae" genus="Coptopteryx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="crenaticollis">
<emphasis id="5AD2EAF0FFD529797019E56C3AD4FDB4" box="[580,743,531,555]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">C. crenaticollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
” is a 
<emphasis id="5AD2EAF0FFD529797179E56C3B88FDB4" box="[804,955,531,555]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">nomen nudum</emphasis>
however, and 
<taxonomicName id="AFA64D61FFD52979735CE54C39A0FDD4" authorityName="Saussure" authorityYear="1869" box="[257,403,563,587]" class="Insecta" family="Coptopterygidae" genus="Coptopteryx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Mantodea" pageId="2" pageNumber="263" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="claraziana">
<emphasis id="5AD2EAF0FFD52979735CE54C39A0FDD4" box="[257,403,563,587]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="263">C. claraziana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is the valid name.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
